      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\" class=\"has-continuation\">where the discounting is given in terms of the defaultadjusted short-rate process <math display=\"inline\">R_t = r_t + h_t L_t</math>, with <math display=\"inline\">r_t</math>the default-free continuously compounded short rate,</p>",
