      "id": "/page/1/TextInlineMath/13",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">For the continuously compounded defaultable short rate <math display=\"inline\">\\bar{r}(t) = \\bar{f}(t, t)</math>, the no-arbitrage restrictions imply</p>",
