      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">which is equal to the default-adjusted short rate given in equation (1). In this sense, the risk-neutral meanloss rate <math display=\"inline\">h_t L_t</math> is equal to the instantaneous credit spread <math display=\"inline\">\\bar{r}(t) - r_t</math>.</p>",
